msg: Update dav-server graph for May and June 2009.

of months, which people may care about.  Although the absolute numbers,
which we graph, have stayed steady, the % share, which we don't graph, has
increased by a couple of percent during both April and May.  I tend to
believe, then that Security Space's sample size has gone down, but our
